358</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;The continent as a whole now stands united against what I'm going to call unfair trading practices by you know who &mdash;<span style=\"color: red;\"> it starts with a C and ends with an A</span>,&quot; he told reporters on Tuesday outside the White House.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:02:50.000Z","msg":"佛地魔國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d842673173158a9ce46f783ea3dd6a9fd8a9ba","tid":846120,"uid":5489,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:35:40.000Z","msg":"C字頭？<br />\nC for CA LI FRA GA LIS TIC EX PE ALA"},{"pid":"59293493773cdd8b000f02296729e4cbc8e7d42d","tid":846120,"uid":28397,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:38:22.000Z","msg":"Kina"},{"pid":"f3163ce189a61a29826a4dbbce35750130799eaa","tid":846120,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0808cd92f257b88bfa2d2489aeb498d0daaf52a0","tid":846120,"uid":168366,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:00:07.000Z","msg":"California<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:39:27.000Z","msg":"左膠天國"},{"pid":"ba60a72f6404121e6806f76a441f0660bad65ff8","tid":846120,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:41:01.000Z","msg":"CIA <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61af482f84b980e67875568a5679611fe3a38907","tid":846120,"uid":19287,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:44:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.sixthsensesalon.co.uk/files/2017/03/cokeredcircle.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sixthsensesalon.co.uk%2Ffile